<li><a href="/gcf/project/sdgs/1087" class="sorting-list__item"><img srcset="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_8.png 1x, /gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_8@2x.png 2x" src="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_8.png" alt="SDGアイコン" decoding="async" />8.働きがいも経済成長も</a></li><li><a href="/gcf/project/sdgs/1088" class="sorting-list__item"><img srcset="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_9.png 1x, /gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_9@2x.png 2x" src="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_9.png" alt="SDGアイコン" decoding="async" />9.産業と技術革新の基盤をつくろう</a></li><li><a href="/gcf/project/sdgs/1093" class="sorting-list__item"><img srcset="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_14.png 1x, /gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_14@2x.png 2x" src="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_14.png" alt="SDGアイコン" decoding="async" />14.海の豊かさを守ろう</a></li>
